original_title: Brooklyn: Atlantic Avenue - East New York Avenue
text:
(1)
At the intersection of Atlantic with East New York Aves., showing at the intersection a building which in 1873 was known as the House of the Good Shepherd. It was later converted into a hotel known as the Central House, which was kept by Sim Nagel.

April 1929.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2)
The same, showing the south side of Atlantic Ave.

April 1929.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
